Explanation of the mods added by ztronzo:

Strafe Mode while holding fire:

=> You can move around holding fire button 1 to keep the direction of the player while shooting

Allow human players to pass through each other (2P mode):

=> No collision between human players (Human players can pass through each other in 2 player mode)"

